lead_paragraph: Jason Witten stood in the posh locker room at the new practice facility for the Dallas Cowboys, addressing a topic that came up frequently at musty old Valley Ranch — as recently as last year.

headline.print_headline: Here He Goes Again: Witten Says Cowboys Can Win Without Romo
